Package: ralger
Type: Package
Title: Easy Web Scraping
Version: 1.1.0
Author: Mohamed El Fodil Ihaddaden
Maintainer: Mohamed El Fodil Ihaddaden <ihaddaden.fodeil@gmail.com>
Description: The goal of 'ralger' is to facilitate web scraping in R. 
    The user has the ability to extract a vector with scrap(), a tidy dataframe using tidy_scrap(), a table with table_scrap() and weblinks with weblinks_scrap().
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=ralger, https://github.com/feddelegrand7/ralger, https://feddelegrand7.github.io/ralger/
BugReports: https://github.com/feddelegrand7/ralger/issues
